on VarHalfWay var1, var2
  [  0] getparam 0 .............................. <var1>
  [  2] getparam 1 .............................. <var2>
  [  4] pusharglist 2 ........................... <var1, var2>
  [  6] extcall 151 ............................. <VarDiff(var1, var2)>
  [  8] setlocal 0 .............................. diff = VarDiff(var1, var2)
  [ 10] getparam 0 .............................. <var1>
  [ 12] getparam 1 .............................. <var2>
  [ 14] pusharglist 2 ........................... <var1, var2>
  [ 16] extcall 180 ............................. <max(var1, var2)>
  [ 18] getlocal 0 .............................. <diff>
  [ 20] pushint8 2 .............................. <2>
  [ 22] div ..................................... <diff / 2>
  [ 23] sub ..................................... <max(var1, var2) - (diff / 2)>
  [ 24] setlocal 1 .............................. halfWay = max(var1, var2) - (diff / 2)
  [ 26] getlocal 1 .............................. <halfWay>
  [ 28] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <halfWay>
  [ 30] extcall 3 ............................... return halfWay
  [ 32] ret
end
